### Home Page:

- **Information Cards:** On the home page, you'll find cards with basic information about the Judo club. Click on any card to open a dialog box containing more detailed information about the respective topic.

<img src="./Other/Card.png" alt="Logo" align="center"  width="auto" height="300">
<img src="./Other/CardDialog.png" alt="Logo" align="center"  width="400" height="auto"><br><br>

- **Contact Form:** The home page also features a contact form where you can input your name, email, phone number, message, and select whether you're a student or a parent. Tick the box to specify your role, then click the submit button to send your message to the club.

<img src="./Other/contactForm.png" alt="Logo" align="center"  width="350" height="auto">
<img src="./Other/map.png" alt="Logo" align="center"  width="400" height="auto"><br><br>

### About Us Page:

- **Basic Information:** The About Us page provides basic information about the Judo club, its history, mission, and values.

<img src="./Other/timetable.png" alt="Logo" align="center"  width="400" height="auto"><br><br>

- **Embedded YouTube Video:** You'll also find an embedded YouTube video on the About Us page. Click the play button to watch the video and use other controls to adjust playback settings.

<img src="./Other/video.png" alt="Logo" align="center"  width="400" height="auto"><br><br>

### Login Page:

- **Login Form:** On the login page, you'll find a form where you can input your email and password. Click the "Log in" button to sign in to your account.

<img src="./Other/loginForm.png" alt="Logo" align="center"  width="auto" height="300"><br><br>

- **Sign Up:** Alternatively, if you don't have an account, you can click the "Sign up" button to open a dialog box containing a sign-up form. Input your details and password, then click the submit button to create a new account.

<img src="./Other/signupForm.png" alt="Logo" align="center"  width="auto" height="300"><br><br>

### Exercises Page:

- **Exercise Form:** The Exercises page features a form where you can select a muscle group, exercise type, and/or difficulty level. Choose your preferences and click the "Generate Exercise" button to generate a list of exercise cards.

<img src="./Other/exerciseForm.png" alt="Logo" align="center"  width="auto" height="300"><br><br>

- **Exercise Cards:** Each exercise card displays an image, instructions, and other details of the exercise. Scroll through the list to explore different exercises and their descriptions.

<img src="./Other/exerciseCard.png" alt="Logo" align="center"  width="300" height="auto"><br><br>

### Footer:

The footer contains copyright information as well as working links to our Facebook and Instagram pages

<img src="./Other/Footer.png" alt="Logo" align="center"  width="auto" height="30"><br><br>

These features allow users to navigate through the website, access detailed information, contact the club, watch videos, log in or sign up for an account, and explore various exercises tailored to their preferences.

